Ranger Help for: seasonal flux
================================

SYNTAX:      flux <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   9
BASE SP:     variable
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to channel the energy of the current season
into an attack against a target. The damage type and power vary
depending on the time of year. Spring brings poison, summer brings
fire, autumn brings decay, and winter brings frost. A skilled Ranger
learns to read the seasons and use their power to maximum effect.
The damage scales with the Ranger's wisdom and guild level.
